%% Diagram: Structured clone vs transfer over postMessage
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main
    participant SCA as Clone
    participant Worker

    note over Main,Worker: Clone path
    Main->>SCA: serialize(value)
    SCA-->>SCA: walk graph,\ncopy bytes,\ntrack cycles
    SCA->>Worker: deserialize(copy)
    note right of Main: original\nkeeps ownership

    note over Main,Worker: Transfer path
    Main->>SCA: serialize(value, [arrayBuf])
    SCA-->>Main: detach\n(byteLength = 0)
    SCA->>Worker: hand over backing memory
    note right of Worker: zero-copy\nregardless of size
